title: Happy Healthy
description: Single page website created to practice fundamental skills of modern web development. Features sections such: About, Services, Reviews, and Sign Up.  This site uses an energetic color scheme to tie in the brand and is completely responsive on mobile devices.

title: Dog Walking
description: Fictitious dog walking business showcased in a single page website.  This site showcases what the company does, previous clients, a history of the company, and a form to have potential users sign up.  This site is completely responsive on mobile devices.

title: Construction Underwriters
description: Redesign of a website for a construction underwriting company.  There are sections to meet the employees, see company history, find on google maps, and more.  This is completely responsive on mobile devices.
